    "id": "f_csv_7bee2a4c65",
    "slug": "when-we-did-eventually-get-to-the-party-me-walking-next-to-dad-s-volvo-driving",
    "texto": "When we did eventually get to the party - me walking next to Dad's Volvo driving at five miles an hour - I had a horrible time. Everyone laughed at first but then more or less ignored me. In a mood of defiant stuffed oliveness I did have a dance by myself but things kept crashing to the floor around me. The host asked if I would sit down. I had a go at that but it was useless. In the end I was at the gate for about an hour before Dad arrived.",
